Business Brief -- American Dental Laser Inc.:
   Company Sees $1.6 Million
   Loss for '91 Fourth Quarter
The company reported that it has taken strong measures to
reduce expenses. Reductions have been made in non-sales staff
and salaries and executive cash bonuses for upper management
were eliminated for 1991. American Dental Laser said that new
product development should not be affected by the company's
cost-cutting.